No, it's not.

38:37.750 --> 38:39.491
It's smart.

38:40.796 --> 38:42.363
Take the job.

38:43.712 --> 38:45.366
I...

38:45.366 --> 38:47.629
I-I've got to think about it,

38:47.629 --> 38:49.762
- if that's...
- Don't ask for permission.

38:52.504 --> 38:53.766
Right.

38:54.941 --> 38:56.899
I'm gonna think about it.

38:58.248 --> 39:00.860
And in the meantime,

39:00.860 --> 39:03.428
think about what I said.

39:03.428 --> 39:04.994
About Dorothy.

39:04.994 --> 39:07.693
She's out there somewhere.

39:07.693 --> 39:10.130
And she's not asking for help.

39:10.130 --> 39:12.088
But she needs it.

39:19.966 --> 39:22.011
You've got 24 hours.

39:23.230 --> 39:25.145
Or the opportunity disappears.

39:28.322 --> 39:30.280
That's how the world works.

39:30.280 --> 39:32.370
This brief window.

39:33.936 --> 39:35.503
Thank you.

39:35.503 --> 39:37.331
Aw, bet you didn't think
you were gonna say that

39:37.331 --> 39:39.507
and mean it
when you walked in here.

40:23.812 --> 40:25.292
Mr. Dugger.

40:28.382 --> 40:29.731
- I have a call for you.
- What?

40:29.731 --> 40:32.778
Thank you. Thanks.

40:32.778 --> 40:35.563
Danish Graves,
Redemption Services,

40:35.563 --> 40:37.217
in case you forgot.

40:37.217 --> 40:39.088
And I have Mrs. Lyon
on the phone.

40:39.088 --> 40:40.438
For you.

40:40.438 --> 40:41.526
What?

40:51.231 --> 40:52.275
Hello?

40:52.275 --> 40:54.408
Are your balls in your belly,

40:54.408 --> 40:57.237
looking for a safe
place to hide?

40:58.543 --> 41:00.458
<i>Good.</i>

41:00.458 --> 41:01.981
<i>Listen to me.</i>

41:01.981 --> 41:03.765
<i>I'm pulling the offer.</i>

41:03.765 --> 41:05.898
That $100 million

41:05.898 --> 41:08.988
is going to Mesa Prudential

41:08.988 --> 41:12.121
<i>out in Flagstaff.</i>

41:12.121 --> 41:14.689
<i>What you get instead
is the full might</i>

41:14.689 --> 41:17.213
<i>of the federal government</i>

41:17.213 --> 41:19.346
reading the shit stains
in your underwear

41:19.346 --> 41:21.696
like tea leaves.

41:21.696 --> 41:23.306
Mrs. Lyon...

41:23.306 --> 41:25.221
Quiet.

41:25.221 --> 41:27.180
A grown-up is talking.

41:27.180 --> 41:31.750
I called the SEC chairman personally.

41:31.750 --> 41:34.143
And as we speak,

41:34.143 --> 41:36.406
two dozen federal agents

41:36.406 --> 41:40.759
are in your office,
seizing your books.

41:40.759 --> 41:44.023
<i>They've also frozen
every personal</i>

41:44.023 --> 41:47.200
<i>and business bank account
you've got.</i>

41:47.200 --> 41:49.071
<i>So...</i>

41:49.071 --> 41:51.291
I hope you didn't give
all your walking-around money

41:51.291 --> 41:53.511
to that stripper.

41:55.948 --> 41:59.125
Oh. Plus, I-I hear

41:59.125 --> 42:01.040
your son is starting
his freshman year

42:01.040 --> 42:03.303
at, um, Notre Dame?

42:03.303 --> 42:07.481
Except, whoops.

42:07.481 --> 42:10.136
You're late on tuition.

42:10.136 --> 42:13.879
<i>So, hmm.</i>

42:13.879 --> 42:15.315
<i>Oh, that ring you hear--</i>

42:15.315 --> 42:17.665
<i>that's your son
on the other line</i>

42:17.665 --> 42:20.712
<i>calling to tell you
he's been expelled.</i>

42:20.712 --> 42:22.670
Mrs. Lyon, please.

42:22.670 --> 42:24.629
Oh, "please."

42:24.629 --> 42:26.892
That's your secret weapon?

42:29.242 --> 42:31.549
Do you want to know
what your mistake was?

42:31.549 --> 42:35.248
It was thinking
death is the worst thing

42:35.248 --> 42:36.902
that could happen to you.

42:38.077 --> 42:39.861
<i>So, congratulations.</i>

42:39.861 --> 42:42.908
<i>The sheriff's
not gonna kill you.</i>

42:42.908 --> 42:46.564
<i>Instead you're going to live
the rest of your days</i>

42:46.564 --> 42:48.653
<i>in squalor,</i>

42:48.653 --> 42:50.698
<i>surrounded by
the dead-eyed stares</i>

42:50.698 --> 42:53.614
<i>of your futureless children.</i>

43:05.060 --> 43:06.584
Have a nice night.

46:39.187 --> 46:42.147
<i>Now I get it.</i>
